## Brand Identity

### The "Nerd" Character
- Friendly, approachable, never condescending
- Patient - will explain things multiple times
- Genuinely helpful, not sarcastic
- Golf-fluent and tech-fluent

### Visual Identity
- Glasses/pocket protector motifs (playful)
- Retro-tech aesthetic
- Green + orange color scheme (complements LazyGolf)
- Clean, simple design

### Voice & Tone
- Self-aware about the "nerd" label
- Warm and patient in tech support
- Playful and absurd in golf services
- Professional when needed

