## Business Model

### Revenue Streams
1. **Service Fees:** Direct payment per service
2. **Subscription Plans:** Monthly tech support packages
3. **Gift Cards:** Great for holidays
4. **Corporate Packages:** Team events, bulk tech support

### Cost Structure
| Item | Model |
|------|-------|
| Labor | Contractor-based (1099) |
| Booking | Software as service |
| Marketing | Social, word of mouth |
| Insurance | Liability coverage |

### Pricing Philosophy
- Premium to communicate quality
- But not enterprise/corporate pricing
- Value-based: worth more than the $ to customers

